Package structures

Class GroupedDataFrame

java.lang.Object
structures.GroupedDataFrame
public class GroupedDataFrame extends Object
GroupedDataFrame provides grouped operations (sum, mean, min, max, etc.) on a DataFrame based on specified group keys.
